Simple demonstration of real time URL validation.

Dependencies:
RSence 2.0 or higher (http://rubygems.org/gems/rsence)

Usage:
Drop into the project plugin directory and fire it up! 
For example:
- rsence initenv myproject
- drop the url_validator folder and its contents into myproject/plugins
- rsence run -f myproject

Licence:
LGPL v3

More information: 
http://rsence.org/projects/rsence